description.narrative: In 2019, UNICEF supported, through innovative bottom-up approaches and iterative bottleneck analysis, the convergence municipalities initiative in 40 convergence municipalities at community, regional and national levels. The CO also supported elaboration of the sectoral 2019 annual work plans, as well as the 2019 convergence municipality action plans (PACCs) for each of the 40 convergence municipalities. These PACCs cover the KRC and local governance. Another major achievement in 2019 was the launch of the Country Programme Mid-Term Review, embedded in the 2019 Annual Review process, which was then converted to an Expanded Annual Review. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
